body:
After upgrading TF to 1.3rc2, I have this error when starting tensorboard
```
No such file or directory: '/usr/local/lib/python3.4/dist-packages/tensorflow/tensorboard/TAG'
```
I reported the issue at [Tenorboard issues](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorboard/issues/352)
